    "body": "@Qquanwei What do you mean two scrollbars.  If you use CSS similar to this\n\n``` css\nwebview {\n  height: 100vh;\n  width: 100vw;\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n}\n```\n\nThe webview elements will fill the BrowserWindow completely and the only scrollbar will be the internal scrollbar inside the webview, which for all intents and purposes will look exactly as if it was the main windows scrollbar\n"
